 Creator of the Universe, sneezed.
 · God bless you," said the manager. This was a fully automatic response many
 Americans had to hearing a person sneeze.
 Thank you," said Trout. Thus a temporary friendship was formed.
 Trout said he hoped to get safely to a cheap hotel. The manager said he hoped to
