 The manager told Trout a little about what the planet looked like to him. It was a
 place where he had a wife and two kids, he said. They didn't know he ran a theater
 which showed blue movies. They thought he was doing consulting work as an engineer
 so late at night. He said that the planet didn't have much use for engineers his age
